name: Tulala
description:
Tulala (daydreaming) is a writer/ rapper/ performer based in Cavite, PH. He is also the founder of Ingay Likha, a platform and space given by anyone who wants to perform or express their selves thru music, battle rap, spoken word, and even on visual arts. I considered him as a treasure of local hiphop in the Philippines. 



Collecting this and other 1/1s creation means supporting a dream of the artist to continue his craft while making a living.
Join Jakestudyos on his journey and evolution.
